类 HistogramDataPointRpc

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.opentsdb.tsd.HistogramDataPointRpc

  • public class HistogramDataPointRpc
extends Object
    The class responsible for writing histograms from Telnet calls or HTTP requests.

    2.4

    • 构造器详细资料

      • HistogramDataPointRpc

        public HistogramDataPointRpc(Config config)
        Default ctor. Checks the "tsd.core.histograms.config" value to see if histograms are enabled. If they are not, then exceptions are returned.
        参数:
        config - A non-null config to pull data from.

      • execute

        public void execute(TSDB tsdb,
                    net.opentsdb.tsd.HttpQuery query)
             throws IOException
        Handles HTTP RPC put requests
        参数:
        tsdb - The TSDB to which we belong
        query - The HTTP query from the user
        抛出:
        IOException - if there is an error parsing the query or formatting the output

      • importDataPoint

        protected com.stumbleupon.async.Deferred<Object> importDataPoint(TSDB tsdb,
                                                                 String[] words)
        Imports a single data point.
        参数:
        tsdb - The TSDB to import the data point into.
        words - The words describing the data point to import, in the following format: [metric, timestamp, value, ..tags..]
        返回:
        A deferred object that indicates the completion of the request.

      • getDataPointFromString

        protected IncomingDataPoint getDataPointFromString(TSDB tsdb,
                                                   String[] words)
        Converts the string array to an IncomingDataPoint. WARNING: This method does not perform validation. It should only be used by the Telnet style execute above within the error callback. At that point it means the array parsed correctly as per importDataPoint.
        参数:
        tsdb - The TSDB for encoding/decoding.
        words - The array of strings representing a data point
        返回:
        An incoming data point object.

      • processDataPoint

        public <T extends IncomingDataPoint> void processDataPoint(TSDB tsdb,
                                                           net.opentsdb.tsd.HttpQuery query,
                                                           List<T> dps)
        Handles one or more incoming data point types for the HTTP endpoint to put raw, rolled up or aggregated data points
        类型参数:
        T - An IncomingDataPoint class.
        参数:
        tsdb - The TSDB to which we belong
        query - The query to respond to
        dps - The de-serialized data points
        抛出:
        BadRequestException - if the data is invalid in some way
        从以下版本开始:
        2.4
